Package cps.mouradalpha

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CVMBasic
    The class CVMBasic implements the single JVM assembly for our project We have a Publisher, a Subscriber and a Broker in the middle providing its services for them.
    CVMBasic2Broker
    The class CVMBasic2Broker implements the single JVM for our project, the idea is to have two brokers, one publisher and one subscriber.
    CVMBasicWithPlugins
    The class CVMBasicWithPlugins implements the single JVM assembly for our project, in this example we use plugins for the Publisher and Subscriber with PublisherWithPlugin class and SubscriberWithPlugin.
    CVMConcurrence
    The class CVMConcurrence implements the single JVM assembly for our project, in this example we test the concurrency of the Broker with multiple Subscriber and Publisher.
    DataBrut
    The class DataBrut is used to get an ArraList of random Footballeur, it will be used for testing.
    DCVMBasic
    The class AbstractDistributedCVM implements the multi-JVM assembly for our project, in this example we have two JVMs, one of them has a broker and a publisher, the other one has a broker and subscriber.
    DCVMPerformance3brokers  
    Footballeur
    The class Footballeur is used for testing our project it has fields with different types
    Proprieties
    The class Proprieties defines a set of properties used inside the Message class.
    TestVMSystem  
    TimeStamp
    The class TimeStamp represent a TimesStamp for a specific message
